Author: tabunfile
Comment: I added the repositories for blueman and reloaded, but need the GPG keyfile. Where can I get this? I also changed Intrepid to Jaunty.

Author: Phil
Comment:
Well, it might keep asking you if it’s OK to continue but you shouldn’t \*need\* the GPG key.

The keyfile is here [http://keyserver.ubuntu.com:11371/pks/lookup?op=get&search=0x6B15AB91951DC1E2](http://keyserver.ubuntu.com:11371/pks/lookup?op=get&search=0x6B15AB91951DC1E2)

the instructions for adding it are here: <https://help.launchpad.net/Packaging/PPA#Adding%20a%20PPA%20to%20your%20Ubuntu%20repositories>

both those links are from this page: <https://edge.launchpad.net/~blueman/+archive/ppa>
